snippet.title: Azure Striker Gunvolt 3 - Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
The return of the mainline Azure Striker series brings back the sidescrolling action combat of its predecessors as Gunvolt and new sword-user Kirin fight off their foes.
